---
title: Sweet-Soy Eggplant & Cucumber Slaw with Sesame Dressing & Crispy Shallots
description: Eggplant roasted in the oven has to be one of our favourite veggies. The sweet soy seasoning gives it a special boost of flavour and the refreshing cucumber slaw drizzled over with sesame dressing tastes divine.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/675a72e9b3cc8de1f221f757-e8896294.jpeg
